The paper deals with computational complexity of alignment problems arising from recent developments in genomics, specifically pan-genome graphs and haplotyping. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of computer science that deal with algorithms and data structures for genomics (cs.DS, cs.CG, cs.GT), as well as those that deal with computational complexity and hardness of problems (cs.DM). Additionally, the paper may also belong to the sub-category of computational biology (cs.BIO) due to its focus on genomics.
